Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
ecoDisableNet...ForFlatNetlist(25.10)    ecoDisableNet...ForFlatNetlist(25.10)

Name
       ecoDisableNetRenamingForFlatNetlist

Syntax
       ecoDisableNetRenamingForFlatNetlist

       Type: Integer

       Default: 0

       Specifies  whether  nets  would  be  renamed  in  ECO report of ecoCom-
       pareNetList. When set to 1, there will not be any net renaming for flat
       netlist. The net renaming will take place if net name  is  hierarchical
       and  the  terms  it connects to do not fall under the same hierarchy or
       lies up in the hierarchy. You need to set ecoDisableNetRenamingForFlat-
       Netlist to 1 before ecoCompareNetlist command is issued to disable  net
       renaming for flat netlists.

Related Information
              * ecoCompareNetlist

